When you pull someone's funding...they start looking somewhere else.  Make sense.  Where would Diem look?<br><br>
The CIA is and was a form of force.  They operate secretely, quickly and usually very effectively.(without your or my approval)<br><br>
John, you find the suggestion that the CIA didn't need to be in on the assignation attempt (it wasn't an attempt!) and the overthrow (it happened.)  Unfortunately, you can't fire corrupt leaders and tell them to clean out their desks.  Problem is... you change the head but too often you keep the corrupt tail.<br><br>
I often wonder if our idealistic thinking sometimes allows us to oversimplify the &quot;appropriate solution.&quot;  Realisticly, we must contend with those intangibles called greed, power, old hatred, racism, tradition, religion, fear, ego-centric and socio-pathic thinking.  You, by necessity, kill a lot of healthy corn plants when you chop the weeds from the row.  The sooner and quicker you get after the new weed...the less trauma.  If you wait too long to start or nickle dime the operation... you'll loose the whole crop!  The blisters on your hand will be for naught.<br><br>
Thanks for the pardon on my humor...hope you will grit your teeth in toleration if it re-emerges.<br><br>
Best to you John<br><br>
